 {\"sentence\": \"'It's very new to me,' Reilly said about working with Hampson.\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hampson\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 509}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was sceptical at first because it's so new to our sport.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have not heard of anyone else using it, so I did not see the benefit.\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"the benefit\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's not so much psychology, it's more just breaking things down.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much psychology\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 708}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Like when you say a certain trick is scary, you are then building that image to yourself.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain trick\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"that image\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'When you start working with him, you realise, 'Oh yeah, you are really in your own head' - little things can have a massive impact, like doing a certain routine before you drop in so that it feels the same every time.'\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your own head' - little things\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive impact\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain routine\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray recentlyreturned to practiceafter his horror ankle injury at the Miami Open, although no timeline for his ATP Tour comeback has been announced.\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1029, \"e